Assignment 6


We cannot detect if an incoming TCP packet is a retransmission. We can only detect an outgoing retransmission if we observe two identical packets 
with the same destination IP without recieving an acknowledgement packet from that IP.

We can detect if an incoming UDP packet is a retransmission if we observe two outgoing data request packets witout recieving the response data packet.

You might need to execute the tool with root privileges 

All data gets printed at the terminal